    {
        "desc": "Exquisite chandeliers of glimmering metals embedded with shining gemstones have\nbeen mounted on the walls, bathing the large hall in a warm light and showing\nthe great craftsmanship that has perfected the hard rock of Ered Luin into\nsmooth walls. Centred in the room is a long table made from dark mahogany, large\nenough to host a full party of adventurers. The seats are mostly fit for\ndwarves, but a few are there for occasional guests of other races. At the head\nof the table is an ebony chair, almost looking like a throne, where the host can\nsalute his guests with glasses full of fine beverages. Parts of the walls are\ncovered with heavy draperies of crimson, hemlined with gilded thread. A somewhat\ngreasy hearth along the northern wall is used to keep the awaiting dishes hot\nduring long meals.\n",
