    {
        "desc": "This broad, stone hall is carved from smooth granite. The floor is dominated by\na brightly-coloured rug woven from fine wool. Its radiant patterns depict a\nvast, stylized battle. Small dwarven figures struggle, while fires rage over a\nsolitary mountain, and a winged, golden shadow soars the sky above. The walls of\nthe room are intricately inlaid with carvings: scenes of feasts, portraits of\nancient dwarven figures, and pillared cityscapes. The sides of the room fit\nseveral large couches and tables, carved from fine oak and illuminated by lamps\nof shimmering crystal, which hang from the hall's high ceiling. A tall gemstone\nwindow looks out into the avenue.\n",
